    setOpt(option: 'DEBUGFUNCTION', value: ((type: number, data: Buffer) => void) | null): CurlCode;
    setOpt(option: 'FNMATCH_FUNCTION', value: ((pattern: string, value: string) => number) | null): CurlCode;
    setOpt(option: 'SEEKFUNCTION', value: ((offset: number, origin: number) => number) | null): CurlCode;
    setOpt(option: 'TRAILERFUNCTION', value: (() => string[] | false) | null): CurlCode;
    static strError(errorCode: CurlCode): string;
    unmonitorSocketEvents(): this;
    upkeep(): CurlCode;
}
